reviewText:
Played this game since 2001 so my Steam 2hrs on record is irrlevant next to my 500hr+ flight hours in this game alone.

Review in two sentences: Best Fly simulator ever! Even for its dated age its a 11/10 and EA/Disney will not be able to make a better one; mark my word.

However it feels like a cheap port to Steam with:

- No Workshop community Mods;
- XWAU incompatibility;
- DarkSaber Projects incompability;
- Some random issues like locked 800x600 resolution and 16 channel sound;
- No Steam Multiplayer support.
- Only English audio tracks available (I recall the French and Russian audio was amazing!)

Until these points arent fufilled by either Steam or Steam Community members (at least the XWAU Mods!!) I should give a thumbs down.. but the game's just so great it deserves a thumbs up! At least the 16:9 ratio screen is applicable through this guide https://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=player_embedded&v=xV3Vhyrso9Q

See y'all on the simulator... when Steam improves the MP.
